RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pickedness
<hw>Pick"ed*ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
state of being sharpened; pointedness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Fineness; spruceness; smartness.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Too much <qex>pickedness</qex> is not manly.</q> <rj><qau>B.
Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pickeer</ent>⟦br⟧
